https://blog.logrocket.com/how-to-set-up-node-typescript-express/

The source code (index.ts) is first transpiled to JavaScript code (dist/index.js). Then run app on dist/index.js.

Add types
npm i -D typescript @types/express @types/node

Init TypeScript project
npx tsc --init

Build + run process:
npx tsc				( npm build )
node dist/index.js	( npm start )
